Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你看不出來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在看小說嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說是言情小說?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真夠熱鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,綾小路同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.23,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准雅宋_GBK\fs45\an7\frz270\bord1.7\3c&H1A1818&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(95,158)}一年級  班\N\h     平田洋介
